ca.ualberta.cmput301f14t16.easya.Model

Class Content

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301f14t16.easya.Model.Content
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Reply, Topic

    public abstract class Content
extends java.lang.Object
    The Content class is an abstract class that provides several utility methods to its subclasses. The entirety of its functionality involves getters and setters for its members. Content subclasses exist to package and store information including and relevant to a String, body, as a framework for a question and response system.
